TermEmu: Kitty
editor: vim/nvim
Multiplexer: tmux
fileMgr: yazi
WindowMgr: Hyprland
browser: firefox, (ublock + darkreader)

SYSTEM DEPENDENCIES:
  wget,curl,unzip,tar,stow,git
TOOLS:
  fd,ripgrep,fzf

FONT (./scripts/iFonts.sh)
AWWW (./scripts/awww_change_bg.sh)

NOTE:
  - vim dosent have cliboard sync capablities by default
  - for tmux clipboard sync 
    mac (pbcopy)
    linux (xclip/wl-copy)

ARCH LINUX SPECIFIC:
- openssh: needed for git to use SSH
- pulseaudio: for audio hyprland.conf uses a macro
- wl-clipboard: for hyprland clipboard (tmux,nvim uses)
- os-prober,fuse3: for os-prober to find windows we need fuse3
- man-db,man-pages,man-pages-posix: docs for api, c std lib, system kernel
